<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Solo para anfitriones</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/jpeg" href="/img/logo-header.jpg">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: url('/img/blog/blog-hero-1.webp') center center/cover no-repeat fixed;
      min-height: 100vh;
      position: relative;
    }
    .only-hosts-bg-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
      background: rgba(30,40,60,0.45); pointer-events: none;
    }
    .only-hosts-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 5rem auto 2rem auto;
      opacity: 1;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadein 0.8s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    }
    @keyframes fadein {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
    .only-hosts-card h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .only-hosts-card p {
      font-size: 1.15em;
      color: #444;
    }
    .only-hosts-card a.btn {
      margin-top: 2em;
      min-width: 180px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="only-hosts-bg-overlay"></div>
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { user: typeof user !== 'undefined' ? user : null }) %>
  <main>
    <div class="only-hosts-card">
      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield me-2"></i>Publicación solo para anfitriones</h2>
      <p>
        La publicación de alojamientos está reservada a nuestros <strong>Anfitriones</strong>.<br><br>
        Si deseas formar parte de nuestro grupo de anfitriones, dirígete a <a href="/register" class="link-primary">Registrarse</a> y asegúrate de hacerlo como <strong>Host</strong>.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-3"><i class="fa fa-home me-1"></i>Volver al inicio</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
